Package: cppSim
Title: Fast and memory efficient spatial interaction model
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ivann", "Schlosser", , "ivann.schlosser.19@ucl.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")
           )
Description: This package builds on top of RcppArmadillo to provide an API to do fast spatial interaction models in the context of urban analytics, geography, transport modelling. It uses the Newton root search algorithm to determine the optimal cost exponent and can run country level models with thousands of origins.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
